@startuml
title <font size=10>Prediksi Penjualan (Forecasting) Flow</font>

actor Owner
participant View
participant Controller
participant ForecastingService
participant Database

Owner->View: Akses halaman prediksi penjualan
View->Controller: GET /pemilik/forecasting

Controller->ForecastingService: generateForecastForAllProducts()
ForecastingService->Database: Query semua produk
Database-->ForecastingService: Return all barang

loop Untuk setiap produk
ForecastingService->Database: Query sales data per minggu (tahun ini)
Database-->ForecastingService: Return weekly sales
ForecastingService->ForecastingService: getSalesDataByWeek() - Group transaksi per minggu
ForecastingService->ForecastingService: calculateSES(alpha=0.3) - Hitung forecast minggu depan
ForecastingService->ForecastingService: calculateWeeklyTrend() - Hitung trend %
ForecastingService->ForecastingService: determineStockStatus() - Tentukan status (critical/medium/safe)
end

alt Jika user pilih produk tertentu
Owner->View: Pilih produk dari dropdown
View->Controller: GET /pemilik/forecasting?id_barang=X

Controller->ForecastingService: generateForecast(id_barang)
ForecastingService->Database: Query sales data produk tertentu
Database-->ForecastingService: Return weekly sales
ForecastingService->ForecastingService: Format minggu labels & weekly breakdown
end

Controller->Database: Query semua barang untuk dropdown
Database-->Controller: Return barang list

Controller->View: Pass forecast data, summary stats, barang list
View-->Owner: Tampilkan overview semua produk + detail produk terpilih

@enduml
